text: Congratulations to @davidfholt on his election as mayor of Oklahoma City!
Praying for all the victims & those impacted by the tragedy in Las Vegas last night. Thankful for our police & 1st responders on the scene.
As Puerto Rico takes on #HurricaneMaria, our hearts are with the people who call it home.
Thoughts & prayers are with @SteveScalise & others injured this AM. Grateful for the @CapitolPolice & their bravery. My staff & I are safe.
Introduced two more cost cutting bills yesterday: H.R. 2730 and H.R. 2731. Together they would cut tens of millions in federal spending.
Looking forward to joining @mitchelltalks tomorrow on KOKC at 7:35am.  Hope you can tune in.
Coming up next on @FoxNews  to talk about my trip to refugee camps on Syrian border.
I wrote Iran Terror Finance Transparency Act b/c @POTUS should justify easing sanctions on Iran's terror financiers. It passed in Committee!
Going to be on @FoxBusiness tomorrow at 7:30 am Central to talk POTUS' executive action, protecting the 2nd Amendment, and the Middle East.
Did you know the #omnibus protects life by banning embryo gene editing and defending anti-abortion health providers? #powerofthepurse
Did you know the #omnibus Congress passed abolishes the 40-yr oil and gas export ban? We're taking back the #powerofthepurse.
I'm discussing terrorism, women in combat & refugee resettlement with @kforkevinogle on @kfor's Flashpoint Sunday at 9:30am. Don't miss it!
Turn on @foxandfriends tomorrow at 8:45 am Central to hear my thoughts on fighting ISIS and Syrian refugee resettlement!
How do we defeat ISIS once and for all? Tune into the "Tipping Point with Liz Wheeler" on @OANN at 10pm EDT to hear my strategy.
Don't forget to stop by tonight's town hall meeting at @OTripleC at 5:15 pm! Park in lot D and enter College Union Room 1. See  you there!
We can't afford our gov's unaccountable spending. Tune into @foxandfriends to hear my thoughts tomorrow am with @SteveDoocy at 5:15 Central.
Tune into @FoxBusiness in 3 minutes to hear my thoughts on impeaching the IRS Commissioner John Koskinen!
Trump says the Middle East would be better off w/ Saddam in power. I disagree. Watch @CNN's @jaketapper at 3:15 Central to hear my thoughts!
Don't forget to call 405-415-2080 at 6:30 p.m. CDT to join our OK5 telephone town hall meeting. Looking forward to talking with you all!
Join my telephone town hall tonight at 6:30 CDT! Call 405-415-2080 to discuss Iran, 2nd Amndt, PP funding, oil exports, and foreign affairs.
History will judge @SpeakerBoehner kindly.
Turn on @FoxBusiness at 11am Central to watch me on Cavuto!
OK5, tune into 105.7 or 91.7 FM at 5pm CDT to hear about my work awarding Purple Hearts to the six service member victims of the OKC bombing
Tune in at 3 CT to @FoxNews @TeamCavuto to hear why I'm asking the President to remove IRS Commissioner Koskinen #IRSfail
It was an honor to join @RepJBridenstine, @RepFrankLucas, @TomColeOK04, @RepMullin, @jiminhofe & @SenatorLankford  in prayer for our nation.

text: We're talking about trade agreements and Country of Origin labeling. If you live in #OK5, dial (405) 415-2085 to be part of the conversation
We're live on the air! Ask me a question & listen to my thoughts about what's happening on Capitol Hill and in #OK5. Call 405-415-2085 now!
If you live in #OK5, call me with a question during my Tele-Town Hall meeting between 6-7pm tonight! Dial (405) 415-2085 to contact me!
The #IranDeal is over 150 pages & I'm reading it word-for-word. We have to know what's in the deal to know its impact on the US.
Let us praise our military who have fought for our freedom both to gain it, and to keep it since our country’s infancy.  Happy #July4th
Find me on @foxandfriends at 8:45am EDT Sat. to discuss TIGTA’s statement that the IRS testimony to Congress may not have been true.
My heart goes out to those affected by Oklahoma's extreme weather & the families who have lost loved ones. Join me in lifting them up today
Anti-China rhetoric could lead us on a path to a Cold War II. For this, and other reasons, I will vote NO on #FastTrack / #TPA / #TAA
Look forward to talking w/@AlisynCamerota on @CNN's @NewDay tomorrow morning at 7:15am EDT talking about TPA, as well as Iraq & ISIS.
Will be on @OANN with @TomiLahren tonight at 9 PM Central. Talking about TPA, China, my time in Iraq, and how to defeat ISIS.
Proud to see the Senate pass #USAFreedomAct today.  I look forward to @POTUS signing it soon.
Looking forward to joining @hughhewitt tonight at 7:30 Eastern to talk about TPA and why its not right for the USA right now.
I'm commenting on the fall of Ramadi to ISIS tonight on @newsmax's Prime. Check it out at 7:30 pm CDT on Dish (223) or Direct TV (349).
Congrats to #OK5 graduates! I'm proud to see so many future leaders launching into life and pursuing their passions. Best of luck, grads!
Call in with your questions to @cspan's Washington Journal at 7:20 CDT. Looking forward to hearing from you!
I'm taking calls tomorrow morning on @cspan's Washington Journal at 7:20 a.m. Central. Be sure to call in and tell me what's on your mind!
Thank you to the police officers who risk their lives to protect our cities. RT to show your appreciation during #NationalPoliceWeek!
Our hearts go out to those affected by the tragic earthquake in Nepal. We're praying for rescues & resources in the coming days.
It was a long time coming, but I am very happy to see the #FortHood victims receive their duly earned #PurpleHeart medals.
Tune in to @mainstreetradio at 5:20 Central to listen to my interview with @AlanNathan. We'll be talking about the Iran negotiation updates
Congratulations to Israeli Prime Minister @netanyahu on his re-election! We look forward to standing beside you in the years to come!
12 million families use #529plans to help afford college. Obama wants to tax 529s, but I'm voting to expand, strengthen & modernize them
I'm thinking of #OK5 students this week by voting for the #StudentSuccessAct and supporting 529 college savings accounts #edreform
#StudentSuccessAct empowers OK5 families, schools & communities. I'm proud to support #edreform moving in the right direction
Great news, OK5! The House and Senate passed #KeystoneXL yesterday. Now we're waiting on the President #TimeToBuild
Congrats to Edmond Memorial HS for advancing to the National Final Science Bowl. Way to make District 5 proud! #DCbound
President Obama's community college plan will cost $60 billion dollars over the next 10 years. We can't afford an overreaching President.
The President's top-down governing is outdated, unfair & ineffective. I believe in free market economies that grow from the bottom-up #SOTU
Keeping my promise to OK5 & voting to defund the President's unlawful amnesty today. I will not support unconstitutional overreaches.
Our hearts go out to those mourning in Paris. We must actively defend our freedoms against brutality and terrorism.
Congratulations to @GovMaryFallin for beginning her second term as governor today. Oklahoma appreciates your leadership!
Moving toward energy independence, free markets, and economic growth by passing the #Keystone XL Pipeline Act in the House #TimeToBuild
Proud to represent Oklahoma's Fifth District by helping pass the #HireMoreHeroes Act this week. Let's get veterans the jobs they deserve.
